        <mxCell id="CONV_TEXT" value="&lt;b&gt;Component ID prefixes:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;EXT-9xxx&lt;/b&gt; — External providers (Mapbox, BOM, etc.)&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;CBE-5xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Cloud Backend compute (TrackIQ pipeline)&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;CBE-6xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Cloud Backend database (PostgreSQL tables)&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;CBE-7xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Cloud Backend distribution (Tile CDN)&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;OCS-4xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Operations Console Web App modules&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;SYN-7xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Sync engine (Firestore)&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;MOB-1xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Mobile Application Layer (Experience &amp;amp; Intelligence)&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;MOB-2xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Mobile Survival Core (Safety pillar)&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;MOB-3xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Mobile Local Data (Firestore cache + SQLite)&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;CMS-8xxx&lt;/b&gt; — Companion Website (WordPress/Headless CMS)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;spacing=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
